[2.996, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m▶ list_tools — 服务器暴露的 4 个安全工具\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.003, "o", "\u001b[2;36m[07/10/26 02:22:43]\u001b[0m\u001b[2;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[34mINFO    \u001b[0m Processing request of type ListToolsRequest               \u001b]8;id=14582259;file:///Users/acture/.cache/uv/environments-v2/hy3-security-mcp-cp3.11.14-d19486d205a6ad8a/lib/python3.11/site-packages/mcp/server/lowlevel/server.py\u001b\\\u001b[2mserver.py\u001b[0m\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\u001b[2m:\u001b[0m\u001b]8;id=14582260;file:///Users/acture/.cache/uv/environments-v2/hy3-security-mcp-cp3.11.14-d19486d205a6ad8a/lib/python3.11/site-packages/mcp/server/lowlevel/server.py#733\u001b\\\u001b[2m733\u001b[0m\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "  • audit_command: 审计单条 shell 命令是否安全,并返回结构化裁决结果。\r\n  • review_diff: 对一段 git diff 做安全代码审查,返回结构化的安全弱点报告。\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  • scan_secrets: 本地正则 + 熵值扫描候选密钥,并交由 Hy3 分诊真伪、定级与整改建议。\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  • vuln_intel: 查询依赖包/CVE 已知漏洞情报(OSV.dev),并交由 Hy3 综合为中文安全通告。\r\n"]
